---
title: Golden Coconut Shrimp with Green Onion Rice and Stir-Fried Veggies
description: Get ready for crunchy satisfaction from tender shrimp coated in shredded coconut and panko breadcrumbs! No need to get messy with deep-frying, you'll oven-bake these shrimp while cooking up some veggies and rice for an easy weeknight feast.
